# Generated Files

This directory contains auto-generated files created by build scripts. These files are gitignored and regenerated on each build.

## Files

| File | Generated By | Source |
|------|--------------|--------|
| `version-data.ts` | `packages/core/scripts/generate-version.ts` | `package.json` |
| `introspection-data.ts` | `packages/core/scripts/generate-docs-bundle.ts` | `docs/ref-llm.txt` |

## Regeneration

These files are automatically generated by:

```bash
npm run build          # Generates both files as prebuild step
npm run prebuild       # Explicit generation only
```

Do not edit these files manually. Changes will be overwritten on the next build.
